==Swedish==
===Noun===
'''brevbärare ''-n, -, -bärarna''' (or brevbärarn)''
*[[Wiktionary:Swedish pronunciation|Pronunciation]]: {{IPAchar|/ˈbreːvˌbɛːrare/}}
